GLOBAL
- Support for systemd powered distro for turning on/off network-manager
- Support for Android, using busybox or maybe without root
- Encrypted transmission on wifi connection (use of cryptcat?)
	
CLI version
- Add support to wifi transfer by switch option passed as command line argument or something else (if a ip address is specified use wifi, otherwise use cable connection)

GUI version
- New gui (portable and platfom-indipendent) with a single window that allow to specify all the parameters (ip address, port used, cable/wifi switch, directory or single file selection)
- Support for directory transfer
